---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

// This page is not linked from navigation — access via /roadmap/ directly
---

<BaseLayout
  title="1px.com Roadmap"
  description="Internal roadmap for 1px.com development."
>
  <article>
    <h1>1px.com Roadmap</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-style: italic;">This page is not linked from navigation. Internal use only.</p>

    <h2>Priority 1 — Tracking & Discoverability</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Google Analytics 4 (GA4) — G-PTGMYXRG60 ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Google Search Console — verified ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Bing Webmaster Tools — verified ✓</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Priority 2 — Social Preview (OG Image)</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Design a proper OG image (1200×630) — not auto-generated SVG-to-PNG</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Per-page OG images (spacer-gif, css-borders, px-unit, power-of-one)</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Test with Facebook Sharing Debugger, Twitter Card Validator, LinkedIn Post Inspector</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Priority 3 — Favicon</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Favicon: 3×3 pixel grid with highlighted center pixel ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Apple-touch-icon 180×180 ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Web manifest (site.webmanifest) ✓</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Priority 4 — Visual Design Overhaul</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Hero section — more visual impact, maybe animated pixel grid or spacer.gif reference</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Content cards — add visual icons or illustrations</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Typography polish — heading hierarchy, better whitespace rhythm</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Code blocks — syntax highlighting via Shiki (build-time, dual light/dark theme) ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> CTA design — more compelling "Make an Offer" treatment</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Color palette refinement</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Page transitions or subtle scroll animations (CSS-only)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Priority 5 — Content & SEO</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Internal linking audit — ensure all cross-links are in place</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Add more long-tail content pages (spacer.gif generator, CSS unit converter, etc.)</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Image alt text audit</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Page speed audit (Lighthouse)</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Add hreflang if Danish version is added later</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Priority 6 — Domain Profile Page (/about-this-domain/)</h2>
    <p>Dedikeret side der sælger domænet med hårde fakta. Giver troværdighed og SEO-juice fra domain-age signals.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Domain grunddata</strong> — registreringsdato, alder, registrar, TLD-stats ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Hvad gør 1px.com unikt</strong> — 3 tegn, semantisk mening, kulturel reference, universelt læsbart ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Domæne-alder som ranking signal</strong> — vis at domænet har eksisteret siden spacer.gif-æraen ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>WHOIS-data highlights</strong> — creation date, expiry, clean history (ingen spam/malware) ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Sammenlignelige salg</strong> — value-driver-sektion (pattern, character quality, meaning) i stedet for pris-tabel, for ikke at anchore $18K-prisen forkert mod $500K+ LLL-comps ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Brandpotentiale</strong> — use cases: design tool, CSS framework, creative agency, pixel art platform ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Teknisk SEO-værdi</strong> — vis domænets Lighthouse scores, schema markup, content authority ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> <strong>Traffic potential</strong> — type-in traffic, exact-match keyword value for "1px"</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>WHOIS Data (researched)</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Creation Date:</strong> 4. maj 2002 — 24 år gammelt, registreret midt i spacer.gif-æraen</li>
      <li><strong>Expiry Date:</strong> 4. maj 2029 — betalt 3+ år frem</li>
      <li><strong>Alder:</strong> 24 år gør det til et "aged domain" med fuld trust hos søgemaskiner</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Priority 7 — Interactive Storytelling</h2>
    <p>User interactions that dramatize the early web era. Must stay within Lighthouse 100 budget (no heavy JS, build-time or vanilla).</p>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Pioneer quotes</strong> — hover/tap-reveal citater fra David Siegel, Steve Jobs, Håkon Wium Lie & Bert Bos placeret i artiklerne via &lt;PioneerQuote&gt; komponent ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Before/after retina slider</strong> — &lt;RetinaCompare&gt; komponent på /1px-css-borders/ med dragbar slider mellem 1x heavy og Retina hairline rendering. Pure CSS + inline script ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <strong>Interactive web-history timeline</strong> — /history/-side med horizontal scroll-snap gennem 14 milepæle fra 1989–2024. Hver har år, anekdote og pixel-artefakt (spacer.gif checker, WHOIS-record, border-ratio demo, osv.) ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> <strong>Spacer.gif layout playground</strong> — live-editor med drag-handles på 1×1 gif, se HTML-tabel og renderet layout side-by-side. Overlapper med backlog-item ovenfor.</li>
      <li style="text-decoration: line-through; opacity: 0.5;"><strong>Era-skifter (retro mode)</strong> — <em>descoped:</em> gimmick-risiko på et premium-salgssite; historien fortælles allerede via /history/ timelinen.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Priority 8 — Domain Sale Optimization</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> A/B test CTA copy and placement</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Consider adding a contact form (Cloudflare Workers)</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Price anchoring strategy</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Ideas / Backlog</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Interactive spacer.gif demo — drag to resize a table layout</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> "View source" easter egg showing table-based layout</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> ASCII art i HTML source — "Here since the table days" ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Pixel art creator tool (generate traffic)</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> CSS unit converter tool</li>
      <li style="text-decoration: line-through; opacity: 0.5;">Retro mode toggle — descoped (see Priority 7)</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Recently Completed</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Fat footer with Articles + References + domain facts (covers authoritative outbound links on every page) ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Removed duplicate trust-line markup in Footer.astro (now uses shared &lt;TrustLine&gt; component) ✓</li>
      <li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spacer_GIF">Wikipedia: Spacer GIF</a> — linked inline on first mention in /spacer-gif-history/ AND in fat footer References column ✓</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
